faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ba5195fa4e0bc8b3bc437e9bbed3fd01642a04","tid":498123,"uid":161125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:24:49.000Z","msg":"根本好多都係個一代既問題。50後個堆廢老最仆街。佢地生D仔女，即係樓主話個D仆街父母，係個堆廢老教出黎。會好得去邊？到第時佢地生出黎個一代又係咁。無限輪迴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一堆垃圾。Sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"1a0ad0012ee113804ac3d37330710467ef57c071","tid":498123,"uid":90370,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實黎<br />\n香港人只會同更差既人比</blockquote><br />\n香港人應該同比自己更好既人，例如日本人做比較。同更差既人比只會令自己永遠原地踏步，好難有真正既進步"},{"pid":"9b97ed4d606cf6ad9fa35b626d0013def5448608","tid":498123,"uid":43420,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:30:15.000Z","msg":"做sales就知香港d垃圾中年女人幾撚On9，真係比少少錢就有得做皇后"},{"pid":"dc1524dabec9944d10588cd5bb570b5ff1049ff3","tid":498123,"uid":105746,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"香港人先難服侍<br />\n成日都想燒鵝味道蔗渣價錢<br />\n有理冇理都投訴咗先"},{"pid":"1cd3dca6f6bd83cfb9b06b489febacc13cf8b7e8","tid":498123,"uid":1444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nop 啲staff 真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前去 要同成班大陸哩迫嗰個咩咩海洋列車 <br />\n<br />\n個staff 見我哋係香港人即刻比我入最前個卡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然係件小事但都覺得好窩心"},{"pid":"fa80c593fee7007cb785c21e7f70cd3a0528453c","tid":498123,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"554f443b4c19d84d2bc8eca2014e77647459f01f","tid":498123,"uid":45696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"不嬲架啦<br />\n班垃圾港豬比你話多兩句諗都唔諗就投訴你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2290bd317dafd12b7aaf3313936ba9359a47d86e","tid":498123,"uid":136430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"做零售，港客又西又冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fb4c5c7dfb68de43aaeb52f1608f0ceacf7319","tid":498123,"uid":56716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實山下RAO PT新返左幾日工好易搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你真係唔怕俾人起你底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戇鳩 垃圾工有咩所謂</blockquote><br />\n不過咁講，啲大媽係就係任屌唔嬲，不過正宗屌極都唔化，永遠嘅troublemaker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 南亞裔都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港客係西，不過對住佢地笑笑下俾唔到位佢地入，始終工作上搞着你嘅麻煩一定少過大陸客同南亞裔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸閪係無文化，搞都係當面搞你，搞完就算，有時你鬧佢仲笑笑口同你講唔好意思。香港人就算你對住佢笑笑口，佢表面無野但事後會投訴。"},{"pid":"68cf57691984f4c9028b02d580100c5be385def9","tid":498123,"uid":75421,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"部分香港人真係好無禮貌<br />\n以為自己有錢就係大帝<br />\n人地職員同你打聲招呼講你好 byebye<br />\n啲西客就高高在上 好似同你say返hi講返bye都嘥佢時間咁<br />\n人與人之間相處都係講尊重<br />\n我尊重你 你有無尊重我?<br />\n你有呀媽生 我就無呀媽生既?!<br />\n<br />\n自己無料到就投訴篤人背脊<br />\n咁夠薑不如當口當面講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正因為部分香港人唔識講道理 所以先多投訴 講晒歪理要人聽佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都要多謝香港啲老闆縱左咁多西客出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038ec68ab91bba582285edc7534fc3135206cb36","tid":498123,"uid":46547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"香港人最興架啦<br />\n自己無禮貌兼聲大夾